 dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic003353.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\" cert=\"low\"/> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" cert=\"low\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>L\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ucio\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/supplied> Sempro\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">nio\u003C/supplied> \u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\" cert=\"low\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\" cert=\"low\"/> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" cert=\"low\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>L\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>uci\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" cert=\"low\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>f\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ilio\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">A\u003C/supplied>tratin\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">o\u003C/supplied> \u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\" cert=\"low\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">a\u003C/supplied>ug\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>uri\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>imp\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>eratori\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\" cert=\"low\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" cert=\"low\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>M\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>arcus\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">Liv\u003C/supplied>ius \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>M\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>arci\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>f\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ilius\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> Optat\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">us\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>sui \u003Cw part=\"I\">hono\u003C/w>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text after Tansey 2008\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>Originally published and restored by Cagiano de Azevedo as a dedication to a Sempronius Atratinus, perhaps son of the consul of 34 BCE, as flamen of Augusta, by the man attested in CIL 10.7501 on Gozo/Gallus. Tansey offers strong arguments in favour of reading the text instead as an honorific for the consul of 34 BC, as augur and imperator, subsequent to his triumph of 21 BCE.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>2008.0602\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1969-1970.0204\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Cagiano de Azevedo\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1969\u003C/date>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/94TF8U8A\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002107\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002107\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Tansey\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2008\u003C/date>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EQIGGH8F\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001478\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001478\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
